dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures.; At head of title: "Department of the Interior, General Land Office, J.A. Williamson, Commissioner."; Prime meridians: Greenwich and Washington, D.C.; Map shows drainage, townships, county boundaries, railroads, military and Indian reservations.
